data.title: The Finale! | Ep.8 | Minecraft Crazycraft Challenges
data.description:
LDShadowLady and friends (Smallishbeans, Yammyxox and Koil1990) compete against each other in a brand new CrazyCraft world. 
Each challenge completed is worth points but every death deducts from their total score. Who will finish the series with the most total points?!

In this episode, I take a random challenges that leads me search for more redstone than I've ever needed in my life.
